{"tid":1754922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[選民登記攻略][2002年前出世既你]2020年立會，我地要再令建制輸死","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T14:41:57.000Z","uid":113124,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ec532ee168225593313512853e005d44535f6a","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><del>年底區議會再會進行選舉，大家必須於2/7前登記為選民﹗今天我以網上形式登記，並寫出方法如下，各位香港人，如果你想建制派成為過街老鼠，就要行動﹗</del></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2020年有立法會選舉，一年後再玩多次，全部後生同我登記做選民﹗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n登記流程主要有三個步驟﹕<br />\nA. 取得表格<br />\nB. 進行填寫<br />\nC. 遞交<br />\n<br />\nA. 取得表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C)_eSign.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C%29_eSign.pdf&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=4029ac43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C)_eSign.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nB. 進行填寫<br />\n1. 可於電腦直接填寫 (若PDF等軟件成功支援直接修改，很快便)<br />\n2. 可在手機上以Adobe Fill &amp; Sign進行修改 (較為難操作，可能我年紀大)<br />\n3. 可利用線上網頁PDF工具進行修改 <a href=\"https://smallpdf.com/zh-TW/edit-pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmallpdf.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fedit-pdf&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=bf60b9c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://smallpdf.com/zh-TW/edit-pdf</a><br />\n4. 可直接列印書寫<br />\n<br />\nC. 遞交<br />\n1. 線上遷交 <a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Fupload_form_reo1.jsp&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=18dc42e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp</a> (但我上載不到)<br />\n2. 直接電郵 form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n3. 郵寄選舉事務處 (香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓)<br />\n4. 直接傳真 2891 1180<br />\n<br />\n網上亦有有心人寫好程式，直接填資料，直接下載成品(但是是2016年作品，不知可否用)﹗<br />\n<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/app.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io%2Fapp.html&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=7cf11b41\" target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/app.html</a><br />\n<br />\n最後我選擇下載表格--&gt;網上修改--&gt;電郵處理<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/18/xj07d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F18%2Fxj07d6.png&h=96bbacd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE教學﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVCEjiY5EvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRVCEjiY5EvY&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJvkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=c66bef27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVCEjiY5EvY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢份文想寫得精簡，其實好快。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n其實我係一個好懶既人，但係呢一次，我真係要沉住氣好認真面對社會當前局勢。場面再艱難再辛苦，我地都要認真、冷靜、小心打落去。愈爛既牌愈要比心機打﹗香港人加油﹗"},{"pid":"4f9e52d52c5cdd90c6dfefa8c7601471a2abe0b3","tid":1754922,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"892daf32a114ebfc14dff617d19438517b1b1b85","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2002年出世既你，而家中六既學生，係呀係你地呀，你地下年有能力改變社會啦</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1a46d2d56ba3797020869b0f9f11830d3e42409","tid":1754922,"uid":36877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"有心人程式有移位問題"},{"pid":"a923b773ff8d658bc219beafd084cef5dac3691e","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1a46d2d56ba3797020869b0f9f11830d3e42409","tid":1754922,"uid":36877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:25:26.000Z","msg":"有心人程式有移位問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"我今年6月尾用pdf修改形式上網表格，就收到信。<br />\n有心人既程式我冇用。<br />\n<br />\n所以係可以足不出戶，唔洗對人，不用寄信地登記﹗"},{"pid":"5391d85cf836eeec3edfafd88347741600eb1a6d","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cdaabd9c3a4fc6f84b74290f3441bd3e195d20bf","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:52:10.000Z","msg":"pussssssh"},{"pid":"93dc80fd0fc8377e058f230a641fc038106a3f99","tid":1754922,"uid":276949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"民政事務處直接填完交係咪都可以"},{"pid":"6ba27b8f21f9a4737d3c718e15c2b635c808bc3e","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93dc80fd0fc8377e058f230a641fc038106a3f99","tid":1754922,"uid":276949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"民政事務處直接填完交係咪都可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"之後你要等收佢既信"},{"pid":"d688d85ce1c6c5361a90dcef87cf1eed53d266f5","tid":1754922,"uid":276949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba27b8f21f9a4737d3c718e15c2b635c808bc3e","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93dc80fd0fc8377e058f230a641fc038106a3f99","tid":1754922,"uid":276949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:53:10.000Z","msg":"民政事務處直接填完交係咪都可以"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"之後你要等收佢既信"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"收信最多等兩個星期左右姐"},{"pid":"c25522c66fe7387f8f0cdd5d4256c24ed1d25ee9","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d688d85ce1c6c5361a90dcef87cf1eed53d266f5","tid":1754922,"uid":276949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ba27b8f21f9a4737d3c718e15c2b635c808bc3e","tid":1754922,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93dc80fd0fc8377e058f230a641fc038106a3f99","t